<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أخرجه ابن أبي شيبة <span class="c2">(١٣/ ٢٢٢)</span> وأحمد <span class="c2">(٥/ ١٥٧ و١٧٠)</span> وهناد في <span class="c1">"الزهد"</span> <span class="c2">(٨١٥)</span> والبزار <span class="c2">(٣٩٧٩)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
